&lt;p>一個遞迴通常由這些東西組成：&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Validity of Binary Search in Leetcode 2141</title><link>https://secminhr.github.io/secminhr/posts/2025-12-02-0111/</link><pubDate>Tue, 02 Dec 2025 01:11:37 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://secminhr.github.io/secminhr/posts/2025-12-02-0111/</guid><description>&lt;p>From the editorial:&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>We can freely use every battery except the largest 4 to increase the total running time. Because we can freely swap batteries in 0 time, all the extra power is interchangeable. We can take this extra power and &amp;ldquo;transfer&amp;rdquo; it to the batteries in live. Let extra be the sum of all the extra power.&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>It seems to me that it claims that the number of batteries in the &amp;ldquo;extra&amp;rdquo; part doesn&amp;rsquo;t matter, but how could 7 batteries with power 1 the same as 1 batteries with power 7?&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Leetcode 3381 跟台</title><link>https://secminhr.github.io/secminhr/posts/2025-11-27-leetcode-3381-%E8%B7%9F%E5%8F%B0/</link><pubDate>Thu, 27 Nov 2025 23:20:26 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://secminhr.github.io/secminhr/posts/2025-11-27-leetcode-3381-%E8%B7%9F%E5%8F%B0/</guid><description>&lt;p>先記錄一下觀眾的提示：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>我們先計算 prefix 來獲得後續計算一定範圍值的內容&lt;/li>
&lt;li>​我們要找區間和，通過 prefix[j] - prefix[i - 1] 可以獲得 i j sum(i ~ j) 的區間和&lt;/li>
&lt;li>​接著我們要推論根據 j 這個位置，滿足題目要求的合理 i 是多少？&lt;/li>
&lt;li>​這邊做一個反向思考，從j往前看&lt;/li>
&lt;li>​先不討論j~n&lt;/li>
&lt;li>​我們可以通過 j - i + 1 % k == 0 這個題目需求知道， i = 所有 5 mod j 餘數相同的值&lt;/li>
&lt;li>​接著什麼樣是我們需要的？ Maximum sum 所以我們會希望找到所有 i 當中 prefix[i] 最小的&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>j - i + 1 % k == 0 應該是範圍 [i, j], 讓我們用 [i, j) 規定 i &amp;lt; j 看會不會簡單一點。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>test article</title><link>https://secminhr.github.io/secminhr/posts/2025-11-27-test-article/</link><pubDate>Thu, 27 Nov 2025 21:32:55 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://secminhr.github.io/secminhr/posts/2025-11-27-test-article/</guid><description>&lt;p>This is a testing article.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>test draft</title><link>https://secminhr.github.io/secminhr/posts/2025-11-27-test-draft/</link><pubDate>Thu, 27 Nov 2025 21:32:34 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://secminhr.github.io/secminhr/posts/2025-11-27-test-draft/</guid><description>&lt;p>This is a test draft.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>